This script shows a simple but powerful parser and highly customizable built in PHP.
It incorporates some classes of my framework that I am currently building (pH7 framework).


###### SERVER REQUIREMENTS ######

----- Operating System -----  
Linux, BSD, Solaris, Windows or Mac

----- Web Server -----
Apache, CGI, FastCGI, IIS or ISAPI

----- Application Server -----
PHP 5.3.0 or higher